Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.98,0:33:24.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.86,0:33:27.86,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.86,0:33:29.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Now, hurry up and get him\Nup on the ship! - OG}{Okay, let's get him up on the ship! - Z}Hurry, get him on the ship!{Rabbit/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.66,0:33:33.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{This is medicine!\NThrow it over him! - OG}{Throw this medicine over him! - Z}Pour this medicine on him!{Gordy}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.82,0:33:36.24,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,It's still too early for you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.74,0:33:39.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,My name is Dracule Mihawk!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.37,0:33:40.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Learn about yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.75,0:33:42.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Learn about the world!{refer back to 10:11}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.04,0:33:43.33,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,And become strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.33,0:33:45.88,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,No matter how many years it takes,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.88,0:33:48.30,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I will hold this seat of the strongest and wait for you. - OG}I'll await you with\Nthe title of the greatest.{Z/Sil}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.88,0:33:51.05,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Surpass this sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.05,0:33:55.43,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Try to surpass[/i1]me[/i0], Roronoa Zoro! - OG}Surpass {\i1}me{\i0}, Roronoa Zoro!{PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.89,0:33:59.64,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro! Big Bro, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.14,0:33:59.64,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.43,0:34:04.15,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,To think that he got\NHawk Eye Mihawk to say this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.40,0:34:07.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Kid, what is {\i1}your{\i0} goal?{The wording should match 07:43}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.44,0:34:09.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.28,0:34:14.28,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{It'll be even harder\Nthan surpassing me! - OG}That's a feat even more challenging\Nthan surpassing me.{Z/Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.28,0:34:17.03,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,How would I know,\Nwhen I haven't done it yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.12,0:34:19.75,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.12,0:34:21.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,He's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.54,0:34:24.67,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro! Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.50,0:34:22.54,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.33,0:34:26.42,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.09,0:34:28.25,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.76,0:34:31.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,L... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.88,0:34:33.13,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.13,0:34:34.59,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.60,0:34:37.76,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Did I worry you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.76,0:34:40.18,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You need... - OG}You'd struggle...{Gaijin/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.85,0:34:46.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{no less than the world's\Ngreatest swordsman, right? - referencing RD 04 - 04:27?}{\q2}with anything less than\Nthe world's greatest swordsman, right?{Gaijin/PP}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.69,0:34:50.65,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro! Please don't talk anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.57,0:34:50.65,Secondary-207-,,0,0,0,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.11,0:34:52.61,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.99,0:34:55.07,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I will not... - OG}I will never...{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.07,0:34:57.53,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{be defeated ever again! - OG}be defeated again!{PJ}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.24,0:35:04.04,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Until the day I defeat him\Nand become a master swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.54,0:35:06.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,I'll never...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.00,0:35:07.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{be defeated! - OG}lose again!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.04,0:35:09.96,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Got any problems with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.38,0:35:13.55,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{King of the Pirates?! - Z- used as an epithet here, so capitalized}Pirate King?!{PJ- shortened for this address}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.14,0:35:18.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.14,0:35:19.93,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,You're a good team.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.93,0:35:22.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I want to see you guys again. - OG}{I would like\Nto meet you again sometime. - Z}I hope we cross paths again.{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.85,0:35:25.98,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hawk Eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.40,0:35:29.90,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Didn't you come to take my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.90,0:35:33.40,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{the life of the East Blue's ruler, Don Krieg? - OG}the life of Don Krieg,\Nconqueror of the East Blue?{Evo}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.86,0:35:37.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{I was going to,\Nbut I had enough fun. - OG}That was my intent,\Nbut I've had my fill of fun.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.78,0:35:39.78,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{So I'm going home to get some rest. - OG}I'm heading home for some rest.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.78,0:35:43.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{You may have had enough,\Nbut I'm tired of getting beaten. - OG}You may have had your fill,\Nbut I'm tired of losing to you.{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.50,0:35:45.00,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,D-Don?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.00,0:35:47.38,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying\Nto keep him here?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.75,0:35:49.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Die before you leave! - OG}Here's a parting gift!{Gab}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.88,0:35:53.13,Thoughts-207-,,0,0,0,,{\t(1317,0,1,\c&HF3F4F2&\3c&HF3F4F2&\4c&HF3F4F2&)}{As I expected...\Nhe never learns a lesson... - OG}It seems he still hasn't\Nlearned his lesson...{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.14,0:36:03.10,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Damn! He escaped...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.02,0:36:13.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.69,0:36:14.69,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.07,0:36:17.41,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Go! I'll leave Nami to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.91,0:36:18.91,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.91,0:36:21.83,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Zoro and I will bring\NNami back for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.83,0:36:24.37,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Make sure you get\Nthat cook to join us! - OG}You just get that cook\Nto join our crew!{Z}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.75,0:36:27.50,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,When all five of us\Nare reunited, let's go...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.92,0:36:29.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,to the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.92,0:36:30.92,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.92,0:36:32.17,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Let's do that! - OG}Sounds like a plan!{Westfal}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.17,0:36:37.34,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,Guys! We ran into some interference,\Nbut the real fight starts now!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.34,0:36:39.01,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{We'll take that ship! - OG}We're taking that ship!{Sil}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.01,0:36:40.14,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,– Yeah!\N– Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.14,0:36:44.85,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Pops, can I stop doing chores\Nif I drive them away? - OG}Boss Man, if I drive them off,\Ncan I be done with chores?{Z/Westfal}{refer to earlier One Pace Baratie episodes for "boss man" as Luffy's nickname for Zeff}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.85,0:36:46.73,Main-207-,,0,0,0,,{Suit yourself. - OG}Be my guest.{Z - Zoro already said "Suit yourself" in the flashback, and the rewrite is more service-oriented now as Zeff's the head of the restaurant}
